Interesting, as weird as it looks to see the girls choice here I think that its possible that some gullible girl chooses like this. But looking at how sad he is, it feels bad looking at it from the male's side. 

I'd like to see the Male lead end up with someone hotter! Decent artwork though! 

@repatte I read about what happened to you and I feel bad man. We all make mistakes and we grow from them. So don't beat yourself over it anymore. If you still feel stupid for what you did, maybe get in touch with her and try to make it up with some genuine goodwill and friendship! Good luck.
